name: STSP: Super Titty Space Prison
description:
Deep in space there is a prison where only the most evil souls go.
This place goes by only one name....
Super Titty Space Prison!

Now YOU find your self under the iron rule of the Warden, The lone ruler of the prison.
Condemned to STSP and forced to suffer unimaginable horrors for all of eternity, can you find a way to escape?

Features


STSP: Super Titty Space Prison is a fast fast-paced momentum based platformer with a high skill ceiling.
Master bunny hopping, wall jumping, and slamming to defeat the prison and your friends!

Features
  • Challenging single player story mode
  • Local and Remote play multiplayer VS mode
  • Multiple endings
  • Six secret collectables
  • Original Soundtrack
